com.versant.vxml
Class VXMLExporter

java.lang.Object
  com.versant.vxml.VXMLExporter

public class VXMLExporter
extends java.lang.Object

External API for the Versant XML export capability. The instances named by a set of Handles (or Objects, if a Transparent JVI user) are exported.

See Also:
VXMLView, VXMLPruner
